 MultiGWAS selects two groups of associations from the results of each GWAS package: statistically significant and best-ranked. The latter equally important to the former as they are associations with lowest 
\emph on
p-values
\emph default
 not reaching the significance threshold but representing interesting associations for further analysis (possible false negatives).
